<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>출석 체크 페이지</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'CookieRun';
            src: url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/projectnoonnu/noonfonts_2001@1.0/CookieRun.woff') format('woff');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #F8F4EF;
            font-family: 'CookieRun', sans-serif;
            color: #5C4033;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .check-container {
            width: 400px;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #EADCD1;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #5C4033;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .btn-check-in {
            background-color: #D6B2A0;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-check-in:hover {
            background-color: #B59A8F;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-back {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: block;
            color: #7A635B;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="check-container">
    <h1>출석 체크</h1>
    <p>버튼 클릭 후 출석 체크 해라</p>

    <a href="/attend-list" class="btn btn-check-in" onclick="alert('출석 체크 완료! 이제 기록 게시판으로 이동합니다');">
        출석 기록 게시판으로 이동
    </a>

    <a href="/index" class="btn-back">← 메인 페이지로 돌아가기</a>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>